Microracers - ChangeLog
-----------------------
http://microracers.sourceforge.net/

11-2005
Second release: 0.2
After letting the project stalled for so long, I decided to grab
the stuff already existed and make something decent out of what.
 It adds:
- a better menu;
- multiple vehicles and tracks to choose from;
- special powers and more track features;
- split-screen multiplayer support;
- faster and more reliable.

11-12-2002
Initial release: 0.1
 It features:
- terrain types and checkpoints;
- simple artificial inteligence;
- dynamic rotation and change of car color;
- easy configuration of car and map through files;
- pixel collision detection;
- efficient smooth scroll screen system;
- simple menu.
